radiographic_examinations.findings: Mild bilateral dependent atelectasis in the lung bases. A 9 x 7 mm appendicolith with a dilated appendix (12 mm) and surrounding inflammatory fat stranding. A smaller 3 mm appendicolith near the tip. Colonic diverticulosis and several likely reactive lymph nodes in the right lower quadrant. No free air, fluid collection, or concerning osseous lesions.
